==English==

===Etymology===
From {{LL.}} {{term|abacinatum}}, past participle of {{term|abacinare|abacināre}}; possibly formed from {{term|ab-||off|lang=la}} + {{term|bacinus||a basin}}.  Probably cognate with modern Italian {{term|abbacinare||to dazzle|lang=it}}. {{attention|la}}

